{"tid":2077052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美增列四紅媒為外國使團  助理國務卿：清理門戶","createTime":"2020-06-24T04:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T14:01:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8af117d5021c237d972471a63922cd0e44a2c9","tid":2077052,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200624/ZPSERKMIUFKRPGLVVWEWVD6ZKI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200624%2FZPSERKMIUFKRPGLVVWEWVD6ZKI%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=466fa38f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200624%2FZPSERKMIUFKRPGLVVWEWVD6ZKI%2F&h=6e82019b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200624/ZPSERKMIUFKRPGLVVWEWVD6ZKI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美增列四紅媒為外國使團 <br />\n助理國務卿：清理門戶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國狙擊中共「大外宣」再有新動作。美國國務院22日宣佈，將四間中共在美的傳媒列為「外國使團」，包括中央電視台、中新社、《人民日報》和《環球時報》。今次是繼今年2月把新華社等五家官媒及機構列入「外國使團」、要接受美方監控後，美方再出手擴大對華「媒體戰」範疇。有美國高官形容此為美方「清理門戶」行動；外交部昨警告美方要馬上停止，否則中方會「採取行動」報復。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：北斗衞星升空 擺脫依賴美GPS<br />\n<br />\n中共喉舌媒體央視被美國列入受監控的外交團名單；圖為北京央視大樓。資料圖片<br />\n中共喉舌媒體央視被美國列入受監控的外交團名單；圖為北京央視大樓。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UISQZMQEZQ6WVS7FOQXO2MYLWU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUISQZMQEZQ6WVS7FOQXO2MYLWU.gif&h=e58c395a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國助理國務卿史達偉<br />\n<br />\n2016年習近平親往央視視察，與員工握手。美聯社<br />\n2016年習近平親往央視視察，與員工握手。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LLTKCAD45QLYRSHI3SPRSS7RIY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLLTKCAD45QLYRSHI3SPRSS7RIY.gif&h=a9d8daee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n央視為歡迎習近平到訪，竟然在大堂屏幕打出向習「表忠」口號。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人奧特加斯（Morgan Ortagus）在聲明中指，上述四間傳媒由中國政府擁有或操控，是中共的工具，。。。。。，美方此決定為「清理門戶」，是「打掃之前沒怎麼注意的碎玻璃」；屬美方「自我防衞」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至今華共九官媒上榜<br />\n<br />\n這是繼今年2月美國宣佈將中國環球電視網（CGTN）、中國國際廣播電台（CRI）、英文《中國日報》（China Daily）及《人民日報》美國發行商海天發展公司五間媒體及機構列為「外國使團」，3月又把這些媒體駐美記者人數從160人減到100人，掀起美中媒體戰之後，美方再度出手狙擊中共在美「大外宣軍團」。至此，被美國列入「外國使團」的中共官媒達九家。中方則於3月宣佈撤銷《紐約時報》、《華爾街日報》和《華盛頓郵報》三媒體今年底到期的11位駐華記者的記者證，禁他們在中國包括香港、澳門從事新聞工作；除此外中方未有新招報復。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅。。。。。。另三家上榜中共媒體昨未見回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XMAAPDSDGOQLHBTUQZPRU47G3Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXMAAPDSDGOQLHBTUQZPRU47G3Q.gif&h=119ff61a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n禁中資電台華語節目<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司中文網指，今次美。。。。。。共和黨籍參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）直指，鳳凰衞視是中共的「傀儡」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/BBC"},{"pid":"7c82b1cec4626d2528ee03ef6ecbd3fcdd8e7430","tid":2077052,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"下一步就係清算中資國企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bede5612e1f17ebda7369b9d4db111e61e9f3047","tid":2077052,"uid":31237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T04:09:58.000Z","msg":"遲好過冇"},{"pid":"69b40023d3bdced3eee08866f76fd71b0e5f11b0","tid":2077052,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"中國有私營企業既咩"},{"pid":"6317706f32bc6db7dec4aca37f567b8c467558a1","tid":2077052,"uid":272422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec07f8ee69574ebab623fb077c8d8e2c119fa3ce","tid":2077052,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"清共諜"},{"pid":"0369071772339793c8c9acb2997703648df4f8a1","tid":2077052,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"台灣唔係中國咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bf905e891acf60905ea9bd2077eaa297b9fc61","tid":2077052,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:41:42.000Z","msg":"中文市佔新唐人同大紀元會分晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"79b5fa95189f648d21ffa7b432ecd89bc220871e","tid":2077052,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79bf905e891acf60905ea9bd2077eaa297b9fc61","tid":2077052,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:41:42.000Z","msg":"中文市佔新唐人同大紀元會分晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"但國安法後香港大紀元會好大獲"}]}